## 7️⃣ Quick Comparison Table

| | IF | IF-ELSE | ELIF | FOR | WHILE |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Purpose** | One condition | Two choices | Many choices | Fixed repeats | Condition repeats |
| **Stops when** | Condition false | Always runs one | First true condition | Range ends | Condition false |
| **Use case** | Simple check | Yes/No decision | Grade/Menu | Count loops | Input validation |

